        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(web-ui): skip hidden subagent picker pages",
        "body": "Fixes #89249.\n\nSummary:\n- Advance the chat session picker through raw `sessions.list` pages that add no visible rows after hidden spawn-child subagent filtering.\n- Stop showing raw total counts when the picker is filtering out loaded rows, avoiding misleading states like `1 / 177`.\n- Add regression coverage for a hidden-only page followed by a visible session page.\n\nSurface area:\n- No public config schema/options changes.\n- No plugin API/contract changes.\n- No new CLI flags, env vars, migrations, or setup surface.\n\nValidation:\n- `OPENCLAW_VITEST_MAX_WORKERS=1 node scripts/run-vitest.mjs ui/src/ui/views/chat.test.ts -t \"chat session picker\" --reporter=dot` -> 1 file, 6 passed, 89 skipped.\n- `node_modules/oxfmt/bin/oxfmt --check ui/src/ui/chat/session-controls.ts ui/src/ui/views/chat.test.ts` -> passed.\n- `node_modules/oxlint/bin/oxlint --tsconfig config/tsconfig/oxlint.json ui/src/ui/chat/session-controls.ts ui/src/ui/views/chat.test.ts` -> 0 warnings/errors.\n- `node scripts/run-oxlint-shards.mjs --threads=8` -> core/extensions/scripts shards passed, 0 warnings/errors.\n- `git diff --check origin/main...HEAD` -> passed.\n\nBehavior proof:\n- The new unit coverage starts with one visible direct session plus one hidden spawn-child row.\n- Clicking Load More first receives an all-hidden spawn-child page at offset `2`, then automatically requests offset `4`.\n- The picker ends with visible labels `Main chat` and `Main work`, count `2`, and no dead-end Load More button.\n\nCurrent head:\n- Rebased onto current `origin/main`.\n- Signed head: `3959889710`.",
